title: Advanced match history not working on google Chrome?
body:
Hey!
My advanced match history on the web hasn't been working for awhile. whenever I click it from the client, all I get is a blank page half loaded. I'm using google chrome, anyone know why? screen shot attached in link. I've tried being logged in and out of the LOL website, doesnt work either. However, it works on internet explorer....


http://imgur.com/a/bVg7k

replies.body:
It's probably either caused by an issue in your cache, which can be cleared with [these steps](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies), or it could be an extension you're running in Chrome.

Let me know what fixed it.
IT WORKED! THANK YOU! such a simple solution :)
